  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/ef822f622c4846718e89b622d5b1cb30.poster.avif?t=1762076361\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/ef822f622c4846718e89b622d5b1cb30.webm?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/ef822f622c4846718e89b622d5b1cb30.mp4?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tactical Roguelike Deckbuilder with ability-based combat, fueled by card synergies. Build a powerful deck to support your hero. Use abilities to wipe out hordes of enemies. Discover powerful combos within the near-endless variety of composite cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/363416a77fb27554682fd77eae06b107.poster.avif?t=1762076361\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/363416a77fb27554682fd77eae06b107.webm?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/363416a77fb27554682fd77eae06b107.mp4?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Features:</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Abilities supported by cards</strong>: Hero has 3 abilities that cost mana. Cards generate mana, buff abilities, and heal hero.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Area effect based combat</strong>: Abilities with large range don't hit very hard. Abilities with high damage don't reach very far. Sequence them cleverly! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experimentation without punishment</strong>: You can <strong>Undo</strong> anything played that turn. Try different approaches with no penalty. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Composite cards</strong>: Combination of interchangeable statuses and cycles produces near-endless variety of cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/7b9352602140dbf84ebf9a349654a6d1.poster.avif?t=1762076361\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/7b9352602140dbf84ebf9a349654a6d1.webm?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/7b9352602140dbf84ebf9a349654a6d1.mp4?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Forestygian currently has:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>9</strong> heroes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>54</strong> enemies (20 enemy types)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>52</strong> card cycles (plus 1 default mini-cycle, Potion)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>38</strong> status effects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >52 * 38 = <strong>1976</strong> cards combining cycles and statuses (plus 2 Potions)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/2a06e15b1e77015f9e15681ab92c55d8.poster.avif?t=1762076361\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/2a06e15b1e77015f9e15681ab92c55d8.webm?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/2a06e15b1e77015f9e15681ab92c55d8.mp4?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/ef822f622c4846718e89b622d5b1cb30.poster.avif?t=1762076361\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/ef822f622c4846718e89b622d5b1cb30.webm?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/ef822f622c4846718e89b622d5b1cb30.mp4?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tactical Roguelike Deckbuilder with ability-based combat, fueled by card synergies. Build a powerful deck to support your hero. Use abilities to wipe out hordes of enemies. Discover powerful combos within the near-endless variety of composite cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/363416a77fb27554682fd77eae06b107.poster.avif?t=1762076361\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/363416a77fb27554682fd77eae06b107.webm?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/363416a77fb27554682fd77eae06b107.mp4?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Features:</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Abilities supported by cards</strong>: Hero has 3 abilities that cost mana. Cards generate mana, buff abilities, and heal hero.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Area effect based combat</strong>: Abilities with large range don't hit very hard. Abilities with high damage don't reach very far. Sequence them cleverly! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experimentation without punishment</strong>: You can <strong>Undo</strong> anything played that turn. Try different approaches with no penalty. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Composite cards</strong>: Combination of interchangeable statuses and cycles produces near-endless variety of cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/7b9352602140dbf84ebf9a349654a6d1.poster.avif?t=1762076361\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/7b9352602140dbf84ebf9a349654a6d1.webm?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/7b9352602140dbf84ebf9a349654a6d1.mp4?t=1762076361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Forestygian currently has:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>9</strong> heroes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>54</strong> enemies (20 enemy types)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>52</strong> card cycles (plus 1 default mini-cycle, Potion)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>38</strong> status effects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >52 * 38 = <strong>1976</strong> cards combining cycles and statuses (plus 2 Potions)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/